## ðŸ“œ Requirements

To run this project, the following packages are required:
- Python 3.x
- Jupyter Notebook
- pandas
- seaborn
- matplotlib
- plotly
- numpy

> **Tip**: Run `pip install -r requirements.txt` to install all dependencies.

